title: Bank of America tabs Kurt Walsdorf for broader role

Bank of America tabs Kurt Walsdorf for broader role Longtime executive will still lead Spokane market Kurt Walsdorf August 13th, 2015 
Bank of America Merrill Lynch has appointed Kurt Walsdorf to head up business banking in much of the western U.S. Article Options
